about.summary: ANSII Color formatting for output in terminal.

name: termcolor
raw_recipe:
{% set version = "1.1.0" %}

package:
  name: termcolor
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  fn: termcolor-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/t/termcolor/termcolor-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  md5: 043e89644f8909d462fbbfa511c768df

build:
  number: 1
  script: python setup.py install

requirements:
  build:
    - python

  run:
    - python

test:
  imports:
    - termcolor

about:
  home: http://pypi.python.org/pypi/termcolor
  license: MIT License
  license_file: COPYING.txt
  summary: 'ANSII Color formatting for output in terminal.'

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - jakirkham
